node.text: In recent months, stadiums became a place to cast a vote in a consequential election, receive a vaccination against a deadly virus, or pick up a meal for a hungry family. #ItTakesAllofUs

node.title: NFL stadiums continue to serve as the heartbeat of our communities.

node.text:
"I wish I could experience this city for the first time."

From the bodegas to the hip hop scene to the rumbling of the subway to ticker tape championship parades, NYC natives @victorcruz and @joeybadass reflect on the magic of the city that raised them.

For the full episode, head to www.nfl.com/citylife.
